        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">The model ignores negative to hit modifiers from equipment or abilities.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Ghostwalk matrix" typeId="57f5-93cf-6d5d-4dca" typeName="Vehicle_Equipment" hidden="false" id="2d47-ca56-23cd-4318">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">The model gains &quot;Move through cover&quot;.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Holo-field" typeId="57f5-93cf-6d5d-4dca" typeName="Vehicle_Equipment" hidden="false" id="553f-886a-926e-46c1">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">Enemies must roll twice on the vehicle damage chart and apply the lower result. Does not work on the consecutive rolls for suffering &quot;Heavy structural damage&quot;.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Improved targeting" typeId="57f5-93cf-6d5d-4dca" typeName="Vehicle_Equipment" hidden="false" id="34d4-53c0-250c-47a8">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">The model does not have to declare its ranged weapons at all targets before firing, and can choose a new target for each weapon.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Jammer" typeId="57f5-93cf-6d5d-4dca" typeName="Vehicle_Equipment" hidden="false" id="3841-27f0-9710-4a6e">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">Equipment such as icons or homing beacons do not function within 6&quot; of the model. Additionally, units arriving via deep strike that land within 12&quot; roll 4D6 instead of 2D6 for scattering.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Spirit stones" typeId="57f5-93cf-6d5d-4dca" typeName="Vehicle_Equipment" hidden="false" id="0cd4-e4ef-6109-4fe0">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">The model ignores the first temporary vehicle damage each round.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Smoke Launcher" typeId="57f5-93cf-6d5d-4dca" typeName="Vehicle_Equipment" hidden="false" id="6bdd-671f-77c2-4924">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">The model can use its Smoke Launcher once per game:
- During normal activation, instead of firing weapons.
- If it has not yet carried out its order this round and is targeted by an enemy unit.
Enemy units can only deal glancing hits with ranged attacks until the next activation.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Star engines" typeId="57f5-93cf-6d5d-4dca" typeName="Vehicle_Equipment" hidden="false" id="a5b5-edc3-3224-4a5c">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="0207-88db-7926-4ba6">The model gains the &quot;Fast&quot; ability.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
